Supports JSON.

Request type (POST)
&r=tm


The user's API key must be present for the following calls to this API.

To bid on a player
&playerid=[PLAYER_ID]&biddingteamid=[BIDDING_TEAM_ID]&bid=[AMOUNT]

JSON
